{"tid":1627652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺球場有私家車圍撞手足!","createTime":"2019-10-05T16:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:35:00.000Z","uid":286329,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0ac58b6bc3861873e6755f6e10aed2e7bbff3d","tid":1627652,"uid":286329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"除左今日運頭塘有手足比私家車撞之外，<br />\n其實琴日北區都有！！！<br />\n<br />\n琴晚(10月4日)係粉嶺球場有架七人車高速撞向手足!!<br />\n之後轉左入粉嶺圍<br />\n點解會冇人提!!! <br />\n有手足當場講到個車牌<br />\n我記得架白色7人車係UZ頭!!!<br />\n有冇其他手足有抄低車牌<br />\n<br />\n大家唔係就咁算呀嘛！！<br />\n佢係擺明係專登撞向人群<br />\n琴晚仲有幾個記者係現場，<br />\n目測一個港台、<br />\n一個阿叔、<br />\n一個後生仔、<br />\n另外仲有一男一女，<br />\n<br />\n見到其中有人全程拍片，推到有人有片放上嚟！！<br />\n唔好放過撞手足嘅仆街！！起佢底！！"},{"pid":"b6d232e7f1f710bd8cd2143eb40222fb024bc0fa","tid":1627652,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e4212d32d295f304559aaf9ef62d279395fae1","tid":1627652,"uid":286329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:17:24.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到<br />\n大家幫幫手丫"},{"pid":"fc5dbc1e3a90dbc12528f41018540ca5b3b0910a","tid":1627652,"uid":207635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:38:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1069c3e03a08c96738e19c2fe2c62b47f47bec8b","tid":1627652,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b2270952dbe4d46f88188aad17267533136fcc","tid":1627652,"uid":35126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr